Liana Bridges https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Liana_Bridges 0 A liana bridge is a suspended bridge made of liana vines. These bridges are most widespread in the tropical climates of Latin America, Africa and South-East Asia. A_liana_bridge is a_suspended_bridge made of liana_vines . These_bridges are most_widespread in the_tropical_climates of Latin_America , Africa and South-East_Asia .
